  "read": "This probe tests whether the local grouped-reduction contract keeps working when expanded from one CTA to a full token/selected/D grid. It still materializes diagnostic probabilities and grad logits, and can either use grouped global atomics or emit grouped route-tile partials for a separate reduction, so it is a schedule-pressure probe rather than the final fused sparse-MLA/LI backward kernel."
